Class sdbdump

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    arq.cmdline.CallbackHelp

    public class sdbdump
extends CmdArgsDB
    Write out the data from an SDB model. Only works for small models because of JDBC limitations in default configurations.

    Usage:

      sdbdump [db spec]
  where [db spec] is:
    --spec file        Contains an RDF description of the model 
    --db JDBC_url --dbUser userId --dbPassword password --dbType [--model modelName]
